      "text": "STATEMENT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Following is a report of the sighting of an unidentified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "object in the Oak Ridge Area by the undersigned. On the morning of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "18 December 1950, the following personnel were riding to their work",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "at NEPA Division, Fairchild Engine and Airplane Corp., in the S-50",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "Area at Oak Ridge, Tennessee:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
