      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "At approximately 0827, while riding southwest on the turnpike",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "just outside the restricted area, [REDACTED] sighted a very bright",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "reflection through the windshield of the car. [REDACTED] who was sit-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "ting beside [REDACTED] and whose attention was attracted by [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "[REDACTED] looking at the sky, sighted the same reflection. [REDACTED] then",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "called the attention of the remaining occupants of the car to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "reflection. Of these, [REDACTED] also sighted the reflection,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "but [REDACTED] did not sight it.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "The reflection was visible through the front windshield of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "car only for a moment because, shortly thereafter, the road turned to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "the right. The corresponding turn of the car so placed the relative",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "position of the reflection that it could not be seen through the left",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "front window, which was frosted. The windshield, however, was not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "frosted and permitted excellent vision.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "The object appeared only as the bright reflection of the sun from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "an apparently metal surface, such as might be expected from an aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "at a great distance. No accurate estimate of the objects size or range",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "could be made from the observation. It appeared to be west-southwest",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
